cakes.name: Chocolate
cakes.cakeDescription: Indulge in the rich and decadent world of our Chocolate cake. This delicious treat is perfect for all chocolate lovers.

cakes.name: Blueberry Cake
cakes.cakeDescription: Savor the delightful taste of our Blueberry Cake. Bursting with the goodness of blueberries, this eggless cake is a true delight.

cakes.name: Cream Cake
cakes.cakeDescription: Experience the lusciousness of our Cream Cake. This deliciously creamy delight is a treat for your taste buds.

cakes.name: Cheese Cake
cakes.cakeDescription: Indulge in the rich and cheesy goodness of our Cheese Cake. This delightful egg-based cake is a cheese lover's dream.

cakes.name: Fruit Cake
cakes.cakeDescription: Treat yourself to a burst of fruity flavors with our Fruit Cake. Packed with a variety of fruits, this eggless cake is a fruity delight.

cakes.name: Kit Kat Cake
cakes.cakeDescription: Experience the crunch of Kit Kat in every bite with our Kit Kat Cake. This eggless delight is perfect for chocolate and Kit Kat enthusiasts.

cakes.name: Pineapple Cake
cakes.cakeDescription: Delight in the tropical goodness of our Pineapple Cake. Made with fresh pineapples, this egg-based cake is a tropical treat.

cakes.name: Butterscotch Cake
cakes.cakeDescription: Satisfy your sweet tooth with the rich and buttery flavor of our Butterscotch Cake. This eggless delight is a sweet indulgence.

cakes.name: Red Velvet Cake
cakes.cakeDescription: Experience the velvety smoothness and vibrant red color of our Red Velvet Cake. This eggless delight is infused with the sweet essence of vanilla.
